&lt;h2 id="一zsh-环境配置">一、Zsh 环境配置&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="1-安装-zsh">1. 安装 Zsh&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo apt update
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo apt install zsh -y
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="2-设置-zsh-为默认-shell">2. 设置 Zsh 为默认 shell&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>chsh -s &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">$(&lt;/span>which zsh&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>注：执行后注销或重启终端即可生效。&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h3 id="3-安装-oh-my-zsh">3. 安装 Oh My Zsh&lt;/h3>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sh -c &lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">$(&lt;/span>curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef">)&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#e6db74">&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>Oh My Zsh 帮助管理主题和插件，安装后会自动切换到 Zsh。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>